sailpoint.object

Class Plugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      • sailpoint.object.SailPointObject
        • sailpoint.object.Plugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject, sailpoint.tools.xml.XMLReferenceTarget

    public class Plugin
extends SailPointObject
    Plugin object to store information about a specific Plugin used by the Plugin framework. This class is used to describe any information about a particular plugin that is to be imported in the manifest.
    See Also:

      • upgrade

        public void upgrade(Plugin plugin)
        Upgrades the current plugin data to match the new version of the plugin. Most data will be completely overridden except for the id, name, disabled, position and the value property of any existing settings.
        Parameters:
        plugin - The plugin.
